♪ Oh, how 'bout lovin', girl
Just you and me ♪

01:08:43.161 --> 01:08:46.747
♪ Take a day
Take a day, yeah ♪

01:08:46.913 --> 01:08:50.585
♪ And fly ♪
♪ Working on it ♪

01:08:50.752 --> 01:08:55.756
♪ Oh, this job has got
the best of me ♪

01:08:55.923 --> 01:08:57.550
♪ Working on it ♪

